            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Best Practices for Photographing Your Firearm Collection</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Good photos matter for insurance claims, identification, and records. Here's how to take them without a professional setup.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-1"></i> March 28, 2026</span>
                <span><i class="bi bi-clock mr-1"></i> 5 min read</span>
            </div>
        </div>
